<h3 id="e695b0e68daee5ba93e794a8sqlite3" style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-top: 1.0em; margin-right: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-bottom: .6em; margin-left: 0; margin-left: 0; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: inherit; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 24.5px;">数据库用sqlite3</h3>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 1.1em; margin-left: 0; line-height: 1.6;">1.sqlite轻量级<br>
2.绿色组件<br>
3.单一文件<br>
4.跨平台<br>
5.查询效率极高<br>
6.使用事务插入速度极快<br>

8.适合查询速度要求较高，内存占用较少的场合</p>
<h3 id="e794a8e688b7e8a1a8e7bb93e69e84" style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-top: 1.0em; margin-right: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-bottom: .6em; margin-left: 0; margin-left: 0; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: inherit; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 24.5px;">用户表结构</h3>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 1.1em; margin-left: 0; line-height: 1.6;">1.user用户表结构</p>
<pre class="xiaoshujiang_code_container" style="word-wrap: break-word;"><code class="language-sql hljs" style="border: 0; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 90%; background-color: #D6DBDF; color: #4f424c; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-right: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0.5em; padding-left: 0.5em; display: block; overflow-x: auto; background: #e7e9db; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;"><span class="hljs-operator"><span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">CREATE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">TABLE</span> <span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">'user'</span>(
                <span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">'uid'</span> <span class="hljs-built_in" style="color: #f99b15;">INTEGER</span> <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">PRIMARY</span> <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">KEY</span> AUTOINCREMENT,
                <span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">'username'</span> <span class="hljs-built_in" style="color: #f99b15;">VARCHAR</span>(<span class="hljs-number" style="color: #f99b15;">255</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">NOT</span> <span class="hljs-literal" style="color: #f99b15;">NULL</span> <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">UNIQUE</span>,
                <span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">'forbid'</span> TINYINT(<span class="hljs-number" style="color: #f99b15;">8</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">NOT</span> <span class="hljs-literal" style="color: #f99b15;">NULL</span> <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">DEFAULT</span> <span class="hljs-number" style="color: #f99b15;">0</span>,
                <span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">'health_point'</span> <span class="hljs-built_in" style="color: #f99b15;">INTEGER</span> <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">NOT</span> <span class="hljs-literal" style="color: #f99b15;">NULL</span> <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">DEFAULT</span> <span class="hljs-number" style="color: #f99b15;">2</span>);</span>

</code></pre>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 1.1em; margin-left: 0; line-height: 1.6;">uid主键自增，标示用户的id，username是用户的名字，forbid标示是否是禁止用户，health_point标示执行多少次违规操作后被拉进黑名单</p>

                            <span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">'submitTime'</span> <span class="hljs-built_in" style="color: #f99b15;">varchar</span>(<span class="hljs-number" style="color: #f99b15;">255</span>),

                            <span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">'user'</span> <span class="hljs-built_in" style="color: #f99b15;">varchar</span>(<span class="hljs-number" style="color: #f99b15;">255</span>),

</code></pre>

<h3 id="e5ba8fe58897e59bbe" style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-top: 1.0em; margin-right: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-bottom: .6em; margin-left: 0; margin-left: 0; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: inherit; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 24.5px;">序列图</h3>
<div class="mermaid" data-processed="true"><img class="svg-image" src="data:image/png;base64," name="691a7bc0dbc0827a412fd7540c7d3b80.png" style="height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; border: 0;"></div>
<h3 id="e4bba3e7a081e7a4bae4be8b" style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-top: 1.0em; margin-right: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-bottom: .6em; margin-left: 0; margin-left: 0; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: inherit; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 24.5px;">代码示例</h3>
<pre class="xiaoshujiang_code_container" style="word-wrap: break-word;"><code class="language-python hljs" style="border: 0; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 90%; background-color: #D6DBDF; color: #4f424c; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-right: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0.5em; padding-left: 0.5em; display: block; overflow-x: auto; background: #e7e9db; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;">
<span class="hljs-function" style="color: #06b6ef;"><span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">def</span> <span class="hljs-title" style="color: #776e71;">seplunk_start</span><span class="hljs-params" style="color: #f99b15;">(config_path)</span>:</span>
    <span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">'''主流程'''</span>
    p_log_conn, p_monitor_conn = Pipe()
    <span class="hljs-comment" style="color: #776e71;"># 启动进程A,分析以前的日志</span>
    p_log = Process(target=create_process_log,
            args=(hdfs_client, config, conn, p_log_conn))
    p_log.start()
    <span class="hljs-comment" style="color: #776e71;"># 启动进程B,监控用户的提交</span>
    p_monitor = Process(target=create_process_monitor,
        args=(hdfs_client, config, conn, p_monitor_conn))
    p_monitor.start()

<span class="hljs-function" style="color: #06b6ef;"><span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">def</span> <span class="hljs-title" style="color: #776e71;">create_process_log</span><span class="hljs-params" style="color: #f99b15;">(hdfs_client, config, conn, pipe)</span>:</span>
    LOGGER.info(<span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">"start  log process"</span>)
    <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">from</span> seplunk <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">import</span> DEBUG
    first = <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">True</span>
    <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">while</span> <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">False</span> <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">if</span> DEBUG <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">True</span>:
        parse_log(hdfs_client, config, conn)
        <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">if</span> first:
            pipe.send([<span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">"start monitor"</span>])
            first = <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">False</span>
        time.sleep(<span class="hljs-number" style="color: #f99b15;">30</span>)

<span class="hljs-function" style="color: #06b6ef;"><span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">def</span> <span class="hljs-title" style="color: #776e71;">create_process_monitor</span><span class="hljs-params" style="color: #f99b15;">(hdfs_client, config, conn, pipe)</span>:</span>
    LOGGER.info(<span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">"start monitor process"</span>)
    <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">from</span> seplunk <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">import</span> DEBUG
    first = <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">True</span>
    <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">while</span> <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">False</span> <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">if</span> DEBUG <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">True</span>:
        <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">if</span> first:
            pipe.recv()
            first = <span class="hljs-keyword" style="color: #815ba4;">False</span>
        monitor_am(hdfs_client, config, conn)
        time.sleep(<span class="hljs-number" style="color: #f99b15;">8</span>)

</code></pre>
<h3 id="e5ae88e68aa4e8bf9be7a88be689a7e8a18ce8bf87e7a88b" style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-top: 1.0em; margin-right: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-bottom: .6em; margin-left: 0; margin-left: 0; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: inherit; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 24.5px;">守护进程执行过程</h3>

<h3 id="e7a88be5ba8fe79a84e5a4a7e887b4e5a484e79086e6b581e7a88b" style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-top: 1.0em; margin-right: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-bottom: .6em; margin-left: 0; margin-left: 0; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: inherit; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 24.5px;">程序的大致处理流程</h3>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 1.1em; margin-left: 0; line-height: 1.6;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;">注：部分可能不太一致, 代码更重要的是对正在运行任务的代码，configure设置的参数，map分配数，失败数,reduce分配数，失败数等等信息进行分析和处理，和以前该用户提交的作业情况进行对比, 并没有考虑计算节点的事情</strong></p>

<h1 id="e5ae9ee9aa8chadoope9858de7bdae" style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-top: 1.0em; margin-right: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-bottom: .6em; margin-left: 0; margin-left: 0; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.6; color: inherit; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 38.5px;">实验hadoop配置</h1>
<h3 id="e5ae9ee9aa8chadoope99c80e8a681e9858de7bdaee4b880e4b88be4bfa1e681af" style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-top: 1.0em; margin-right: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-bottom: .6em; margin-left: 0; margin-left: 0; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: inherit; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 24.5px;">实验hadoop需要配置一下信息</h3>
<pre class="xiaoshujiang_code_container" style="word-wrap: break-word;"><code class="language-python hljs" style="border: 0; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 90%; background-color: #D6DBDF; color: #4f424c; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-right: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0.5em; padding-left: 0.5em; display: block; overflow-x: auto; background: #e7e9db; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;">{<span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">'core-site.xml'</span> : [<span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">"fs.defaultFS"</span>],
<span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">'mapred-site.xml'</span> :
        [
        <span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">"yarn.app.mapreduce.am.staging-dir"</span>,
        <span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">"mapreduce.jobhistory.done-dir"</span>,
        <span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">"mapreduce.jobhistory.intermediate-done-dir"</span>,
        ],
<span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">'yarn-site.xml'</span> :
        [
        <span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">"yarn.nodemanager.remote-app-log-dir"</span>,
        <span class="hljs-string" style="color: #48b685;">"yarn.log-aggregation-enable"</span>
        ]
}
</code></pre>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 1.1em; margin-left: 0; line-height: 1.6;">上面说明每个文件下应该有的属性和值，比如说core-site.xml里应该设置有fs.defaultFS的属性和值，下面是列举两个配置项的官方说明<br>
yarn.app.mapreduce.am.staging-dir: <em style="font-style: italic;">‘’‘The staging dir used while submitting jobs.’’’</em></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 1.1em; margin-left: 0; line-height: 1.6;">yarn.log-aggregation-enable: <em style="font-style: italic;">‘’‘Whether to enable log aggregation. Log aggregation collects each container’s logs and moves these logs onto a file-system, for e.g. HDFS, after the application completes. Users can configure the “yarn.nodemanager.remote-app-log-dir” and “yarn.nodemanager.remote-app-log-dir-suffix” properties to determine where these logs are moved to. Users can access the logs via the Application Timeline Server.’’’</em></p>
